  "title": "styling item with multiple values in a field",
  "body": "Say I have index item with this structure:\r\n\r\n```json\r\n   {\r\n      \"name\": \"alvinsee\",\r\n      \"ra_list\": [\r\n         \"Comparative Law\",\r\n         \"Contract Law\",\r\n         \"Equity & Trusts\",\r\n         \"Unjust Enrichment & Restitution\",\r\n         \"Tort Law\",\r\n         \"Property Law\",\r\n         \"Animal Law\"\r\n      ]\r\n   }\r\n```\r\n\r\nI realise the output of `{{ra_list}}` is a comma separated output. How can I style this into `<li>` or  `<div>`",
